verbose_text: We also found that average bond forces for BBK32 producing GCB966 were larger than for bbk32 deficient GCB971 (XREF_FIG), that most GCB966 interactions occurred at higher bond forces than GCB971 (XREF_FIG), and that GCB966 interactions occurred at a higher average shear stress and shear stress range than GCB971 interactions (XREF_FIG).
